OL,3,CChinook disaster families call on PM
OL,4,Cto attend meeting
OL,6,FThe families of those killed in the
OL,7,F1994 Chinook helicopter crash on the
OL,8,FMull of Kintyre have called on the
OL,9,FPrime Minister to attend a meeting
OL,10,Fbetween them and Ministry of Defence
OL,11,Fofficials.
OL,13,FIt comes after Sir Keir Starmer told
OL,14,FMPs meetings are to be set up.JThe
OL,15,Fannouncement comes after more than
OL,16,F25,000 people signed a petition
OL,17,Fdemanding answers around the disaster.
