OL,3,CChinook disaster families call on PM
OL,4,Cto attend meeting
OL,6,FSeveral MPs raised the issue,
OL,7,Fincluding Lagan Valley MP Sorcha
OL,8,FEastwood who said the Chinook case
OL,9,Fshould be the "test case" for a legal
OL,10,Fduty of candour on public bodies.
OL,12,FDUP MP Carla Lockhart pressed the PM
OL,13,Fto meet with the families.
OL,15,FHe responded: "I think there may have
OL,16,Fbeen meetings. If not, we will get
OL,17,Fmeetings set up. I am being told that
OL,18,Fthere will be one.
