OL,3,CChinook disaster families call on PM
OL,4,Cto attend meeting
OL,6,F"I will make sure that there are the
OL,7,Fappropriate meetings, and will update
OL,8,Fher on exactly what form they will
OL,9,Ftake and when they will take place."
OL,11,FThe move comes as relatives involved
OL,12,Fin the Chinook Justice Campaign, who
OL,13,Fare seeking a Judicial Review against
OL,14,Fthe MoD over its failure to release
OL,15,Ffiles on the crash and hold a public
OL,16,Finquiry, this morning attended a
OL,17,FParliamentary roundtable in the House
OL,18,Fof Lords organised by the Coalition
OL,19,Ffor Institutional Accountability.
