OL,3,CChinook disaster families call on PM
OL,4,Cto attend meeting
OL,6,F"But we would like the Prime Minister
OL,7,Fto be there and take personal
OL,8,Fresponsibility for resolving our case,
OL,9,Freleasing all the files on the crash
OL,10,Fsealed by the MoD, and ordering a
OL,11,Fjudge-led public inquiry without the
OL,12,Fneed to go to court.
OL,14,F"In so many cases involving the
OL,15,FMinistry of Defence, families like
OL,16,Fours are put through hell. Like the
OL,17,Fnuclear vets, those fighting cancer
OL,18,Fbattles caused by helicopter fumes,
OL,19,Fand many other MoD cases.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
