OL,3,CChinook disaster families call on PM
OL,4,Cto attend meeting
OL,6,F"The truth is denied, papers are
OL,7,Fspirited away, dishonesty is front and
OL,8,Fcentre from the department we now call
OL,9,Fthe Ministry of Deceit.
OL,11,F"It's not normal to lock documents
OL,12,Faway for 100 years. It's not normal to
OL,13,Fwithhold evidence and lie and mislead
OL,14,Fformer defence secretaries. It's not
OL,15,Fnormal to blame the crash on pilot
OL,16,Ferror and smear their names and
OL,17,Freputations to cover up your mistakes.
OL,19,F"It should not be normal to have to
OL,20,Ffight to truth, transparency and
OL,21,Fjustice and expose a terrible cover up.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
